1. Customers could optimize the cost of energy in batteries using the designed algorithm to forecast these peaks, predicting the top two hour peaks on a high probability day. 

2.Assist the Customers to go with a low-risk, hedging strategy compared to a higher risk non-hedging strategy.

3.Customers can choose the best battery discharging strategy to reduce the risk brought in by forecasting algorithms and achieve the most savings in their electricity bills.

